descriptionHTML:
Customize your watch face with mezmerizing electricity that dance in the background. This animated wallpaper features HD graphics, smooth animations and variable electricity speeds for a look that's sure to leave you pleased. This custom watchface operates in the background so users can keep the full-functionality of their smartwatch including date, time and push notifications.
Stand out from the crowd with a custom watch design. Download Electric Energy Watch Face today!

Android Wear

When using Android Wear 2.0 on your smartwatch, you will find the watch face by entering the Google Play Store on your watch and navigating down until you see a list of apps installed on your phone.
